	quest.26B3AE1E77A84BCB.quest_desc: ["Se lanci un &9Osmium Bee Spawn Egg&r, &bCharged Certus Quartz&r e &8Sky Stone&r nella Lava, creerai un &eSky Osmium Bee Spawn Egg"]
